Ocilla Industries Inc said itsFlintstone Industries Inc subsidiary obtained a three mlndollar revolving credit with Bank South Corp &lt;BKSO>.    It said Bank South will lend Flintstone amountsconstituting up to a maximum of 80 pct of acceptablereceivables and 25 pct of acceptable inventory as defined inthe loan agreement.    In connection with the agreement, Flinstone was granted asecurity interest in its inventory, receivables, and equipment,and in certain property in Irwin County, Ga. Reuter&#3;